pypov - povray scene description DOM for python

1) Introduction
2) Installation
3) Usage
4) License


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Introduction

This library lets you describe a povray scene using python objects. The
scene graph can be written into a povray file.

Be aware that the whole library is a huge 'work in progress'. If you are
missing an attribute with an element please issue a pull request.


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation

$ python setup.py install --home ~/.local


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage

See example_scene.py.


